OL,7,FThe Southern Trust has recommended
OL,8,Femergency general services at Daisy
OL,9,FHill Hospital should be permanently
OL,10,Fdelivered from the Craigavon Area
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FIt follows a Trust Board meeting held
OL,14,Fon Thursday where results from a 12-
OL,15,Fweek consultation were presented.
OL,17,FThe Trust Director said the
OL,18,Frecommendation was "the only way we
OL,19,Fcan maintain a safe and effective
OL,20,Fservice".
